id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bus1665702621196.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bus1665702621196.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bus1665702621196.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bus1665702621196\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Generate blocks of repeated ProcScript.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bus1665702621196__topic_d93182e1_d93183e1_d93184e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93185e1_d93186e1_d93187e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#for</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Item</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Counter</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93188e1_d93189e1_d93190e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt; Precompiler directives and ProcScript\n               statements &gt;</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93191e1_d93192e1_d93193e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#endfor</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bus1665702621196__section_w1g_rlc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d157222e95\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bus1665702621196__ul_nx4_slc_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bus1665702621196__li_d36443e1_d36444e1_d36445e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Item</var>—constant that contains an\n               item of <var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bus1665702621196__li_d36446e1_d36447e1_d36448e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>—list of items separated\n               by commas, spaces, or GOLD semi-colon (<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bus1665702621196__li_d36449e1_d36450e1_d36451e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Counter</var>—constant containing a\n               sequential number, starting with 0, identifying the position of item of\n                  <var class=\"keyword varname\">Item</var> in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93206e1_d93207e1_d93208e1\">Both <var class=\"keyword varname\">Item</var> and\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Counter</var> are defined only during processing of the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#for</span> block.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bus1665702621196__section_rl5_tlc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d157222e143\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93212e1_d93213e1_d93214e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#for</span> directive generates a\n            repeating block of ProcScript for each item in a list.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bus1665702621196__section_mxz_wlc_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d157222e155\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93215e1_d93216e1_d93217e1\">In the following example, the compile-time constant\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;MYLIST&gt;</code> has been defined as <code class=\"ph codeph\">A,B,C</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bus1665702621196__pre_i51_ylc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#for ITEM = (&lt;MYLIST&gt;), COUNTER\n message \"Element &lt;COUNTER&gt; in the list is &lt;ITEM&gt;\"\n#endfor\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bus1665702621196__p_d93218e1_d93219e1_d93220e1\">The ProcScript generated by this\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#for</span> block is:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bus1665702621196__pre_k51_ylc_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">message \"Element 0 in the list is A\"\nmessage \"Element 1 in the list is B\"\nmessage \"Element 2 in the list is C\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612229\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612229\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#for Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Generate blocks of repeated ProcScript. #for Item = ( List ) { , Counter } < Precompiler directives and ProcScript statements > #endfor Parameters Item —constant that contains an item of List . List —list of items separated by commas, spaces, or GOLD semi-colon ( ; ) Counter —constant containing a sequential number, starting with 0, identifying the position of item of Item in the List Both Item and Counter are defined only during processing of the #for block. Description The #for directive generates a repeating block of ProcScript for each item in a list. Example In the following example, the compile-time constant <MYLIST> has been defined as A,B,C : #for ITEM = (<MYLIST>), COUNTER message \"Element <COUNTER> in the list is <ITEM>\" #endfor Copy The ProcScript generated by this #for block is: message \"Element 0 in the list is A\" message \"Element 1 in the list is B\" message \"Element 2 in the list is C\" Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}